high_descs: Move to the cabinet to the left of the sink to the right of the stove.
Retrieve the plate from the bottom cabinet and close the door.
Move to the sink to your right,
Place the plate inside and run some water before picking it up and turning off the water.
Move to the wooden self to the left of the stove.
Place the plate on the wooden shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate on the wooden shelf.

high_descs: Head left to the white fridge, hang a left and cross the room to reach the counter top next to the stove.
Open the lower cabinet doors, pick up a dirty white plate from inside the cabinet, and close the doors.
Turn around and hang a left to reach the sink.
Put the plate inside the sink in the middle, fill the sink with water to rinse it and pick up the clean plate.
Turn around, cross the room to the wall and turn right to face the wooden shelves.
Place the plate on the middle wooden shelf to the left of the red object and behind the blue object.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean plate on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the salt shaker on the counter.
Pull open the cabinet below the salt shaker and take out the dirty plate.
Turn right towards the sink.
Place the plate in the sink, wash it, and take it back out.
Turn around towards the wooden shelves on your right.
Place the plate next to the red vase on the shelves.
anns.task_desc: Place the cleaned plate on the shelves.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the counter to the right of the stove top.
Open the cabinet below the counter and take out the dirty plate.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the plate in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to the shelves on the right against the wall.
Put the plate on the middle shelf, behind the water bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned plate on a shelf in the kitchen.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the cabinet to the right of the oven.
Pick up the plate in the cabinet to the right of the oven.
Turn to your right and walk to the sink.
Rinse the plate in the sink and then pick the plate up from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the brown shelf in the corner.
Place the plate on the middle brown shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean plate on the brown shelf with a kettle on it.

high_descs: Turn to your left move forward and head to the cabinet beside the stove
Open the cabinet and pick up the dirty plate then close the cabinet
Turn to your right then move forward turn left to the sink
Put the dirty plate in the sink and rinse it
Pick up the clean plate, then turn around to your left head to the shelf
Put the clean plate on the shelf beside the red container
anns.task_desc: Clean the dirty plate on the sink going to the shelf
